AI Appraisal + Custodial Library + Credit Transfer Protocol v1.0

Purpose

Create a generalized system that:
	•	appraises contributed assets with AI
	•	stores them in a trusted custodial pool
	•	issues credits based on contributed value
	•	lets users redeem those credits for access to other assets

This is not just resale, not just rental, and not just bartering.

It is:

value capture at intake, value conservation in ledger, value re-expression through access

⸻

