2. General Formula

A simple starting valuation model:

value = market_comp * condition * completeness * authenticity * demand_modifier - storage_cost_adjustment

Where:
	•	market_comp = current comparable market value
	•	condition = quality score
	•	completeness = missing pieces / contents
	•	authenticity = confidence multiplier
	•	demand_modifier = circulation desirability
	•	storage_cost_adjustment = penalty for costly custody

This can later become a learned model.

