8. Risk Model

Key failure modes:
	•	fake items
	•	overvaluation
	•	credit inflation
	•	damage in custody
	•	damage on return
	•	category drift
	•	demand imbalance
	•	hoarding of premium inventory

Mitigations:
	•	visible appraisal rules
	•	bounded issuance
	•	human review thresholds
	•	custody logs
	•	insurance pool
	•	queueing and reservation policy
	•	liquidity-based credit modifiers

