9. Strongest New Insight

This idea is bigger than exchange.

It is a protocol for:

converting static ownership into dynamic access

That matters because access often beats ownership in efficiency.

So the deeper doctrine is:

The system should remember what you contributed, not force you to keep the exact form of that value forever.

That’s a very Money Bin idea.

